{"tid":2206040,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"送貨員六度塗鴉促林鄭下台 遭錢禮判監三星期","createTime":"2020-09-17T08:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T08:58:38.000Z","uid":184261,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4eb7b733d1991f17774c1c195eb4b40f5853d45c","tid":2206040,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T08:38:19.000Z","msg":"送貨員不滿逃犯條例修訂及政府施政，去年5月至今年3月間在香港及新界六處地方的外牆、屏障及電箱，噴上「林鄭下台，赤娥禍港」及「平反六四」等字眼，最終在今年4月被捕。他早前於東區裁判法院承認六項刑事毀壞罪，主任裁判官錢禮指控罪嚴重，不能以對政府不滿作為犯案藉口，判囚三星期。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200917/I3BLGHGSQNAN5ML7UY3F54XS5M/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0K3jkDCCWHAoi3XaRcPbaNUOjQJ2nLYPt6GM88bKzuWJRiDugPMLXH7E0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200917%2FI3BLGHGSQNAN5ML7UY3F54XS5M%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0K3jkDCCWHAoi3XaRcPbaNUOjQJ2nLYPt6GM88bKzuWJRiDugPMLXH7E0&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=9fbcd3cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200917%2FI3BLGHGSQNAN5ML7UY3F54XS5M%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0K3jkDCCWHAoi3XaRcPbaNUOjQJ2nLYPt6GM88bKzuWJRiDugPMLXH7E0&h=74e1a53b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200917/I3BLGHGSQNAN5ML7UY3F54XS5M/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0K3jkDCCWHAoi3XaRcPbaNUOjQJ2nLYPt6GM88bKzuWJRiDugPMLXH7E0</a>"},{"pid":"306c6bb726e07bfbdc8bbe0bfb3e17e0bcbc1275","tid":2206040,"uid":184261,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T08:38:47.000Z","msg":"只有好人先有罪嘅年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" c